      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SPRING MARILYN (6) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing fifth (20.45) in a Grade 5 at this track. Form here sound including two wins. Has claims if she runs up to expectations. STAY TIPSY (7) has mixed form recently, finishing fourth (18.84) in a Grade 5 at Wagga latest but did run well two back when in the frame. Good beginner but will need a little luck early crossing from on outside draw. Can feature with the right run. JACOBITE BATTLE (2) turned in a plain run last time when seventh at Gunnedah over 431m behind Walk The Talk (25.91) in a Grade 5. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and four minor placings to her credit. Expected to run well. BEERS AND BANTER (1) has a solid strike rate from this box.",
